deals.title: Nam Noodle Soup (Pho Nam)
deals.itemDescription: Smooth rice noodles in beef broth topped with stewed beef sirloin, served with a side of vegetables, bean sprouts, and onions. Pho noodle soup (pho) is a famous traditional dish and specialty of Vietnam. It is made from smooth rice noodles, tender beef or chicken, and the flavorous broth which has been steamed for hours. Pho is not only delicious but also carries the essence of Vietnamese culinary culture.
